description:
People! We miss playing for you SO MUCH. The next best thing we could do is create a special show with sublime Directors, Molten Jets/Intergalactic. The Franc Moody Live experience... in a lift! We're using the occasion to raise money for the Music Venue Trust’s #saveourvenues campaign. Please watch the video and show appreciation by donating to this great cause! It's worth it! 🚀🚀

We also have a Limited Edition 'Live in the Lift' Tee and Merch line, available until Monday only. All proceeds will also go to support the #saveourvenues campaign by the Music Venue Trust. 

Crowdfunder: https://liveintheliftfundraiser.lnk.to/1qBSWq5MIN
